  "webview_risks": "No impact on WebView applications. The policy shipping with a default of allow * would avoid breaking any webapp that uses focus APIs and make it an opt-in feature for web developers.\n\nAlso the implementation has a base::Feature (BlockingFocusWithoutUserActivation) killswitch that can be flipped off in case of compat issues.",
